{"tid":1235030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應警民衝突暴動定性 曾偉雄：須按法律分類","createTime":"2019-06-17T04:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:01:40.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2353bc3f45022a95dd9a1cb5bf31324401525f19","tid":1235030,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"金鐘上周三因為示威者反對修訂逃犯條例，與警方發生衝突，政府及警方事後將事件定性為暴動。<br />\n<br />\n警務處前處長曾偉雄被問到，有意見要求更改暴動的定性，他以手機短訊回覆本台，表示香港作為一個法治社會，違法行為必須按法律分類。若有人認為特區政府和警方就事件的定性法理上不洽當，可提出自己的法律觀點，以便社會作出客觀和公正的評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/回應警民衝突暴動定性-曾偉雄指違法行為須按法律分類-041700933.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7-%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84%E6%8C%87%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E9%A0%88%E6%8C%89%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%88%86%E9%A1%9E-041700933.html&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=c331deee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/回應警民衝突暴動定性-曾偉雄指違法行為須按法律分類-041700933.html</a>"},{"pid":"ec65550715bc20cf505cb3b3c630a6daa337295d","tid":1235030,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"咁黑警打人就係酷刑罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f396f0476f5f75e792dfcb4a5c43eaa7c1e2c639","tid":1235030,"uid":31267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec65550715bc20cf505cb3b3c630a6daa337295d","tid":1235030,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"咁黑警打人就係酷刑罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"直頭謀殺"}]}